``` js
var a = [];
a[0]=0;
a[10000]=10000;
a.non_numeric_property="zzz";
var j = JSON.stringify(a);
```

Also I think that support for sparse arrays assume next syntax (not only [,,,,5,,,2]:
`[0:0,10000:10000,non_numeric_property:"zzz"/*why not?*/]`
